This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image synthesis and appearance preservation. It could also belong to graphics (cs.GR) as it involves generating realistic images. Additionally, it involves the use of generative models and discriminators, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves experiments and evaluation, which could place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
